title: LABORERS This is a physically demanding and fast paced (pic)
text:
LABORERS This is a physically demanding and fast paced ad date: 10/21/2015 
LABORERS This is a physically demanding and fast paced work environment. Must be able to lift/stack 50#s or more. Required to shovel/rake/broom wood waste, clear and unplug conveyors, operate chainsaw, stack and pile lumber. Must be able to work any schedule, weekends, overtime and holidays. Post offer drug test and social security verification required. Hourly rate starts at $14.70 + benefit pkg. Qualified applicants may apply at 14980 Camage Ave in Sonora on Tuesday, October 27th from 4:00 pm to 6:00 pm only. We are a drug and tobacco free workplace. An EOE including disabled and veterans.
